        p Forgot your Password? submit a PATCH Request with your new password and passwordConfirm to #{url}. If you didn't with create any request regarding Forgot Password plz ignore this email.
        p (WebSite for this action is not implemented)
        table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
            td(align='left')
                table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                tbody
                    tr
                    td
                        a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset Your Password
        p If you need any help with booking your next tour, please don't hesitate to contact me!
        p - Vanshaj Tiwari, CEO
